channel.title: Send songs/samples you might want to collab on!
channel.description: I want to take a break from my current songs and work on some new stuff. If anyone has anything that they'd like to see me put my Eswyn twist onto, feel free to send it to me. I won't post it anywhere without permission, and if you like it, we can do a collab. I feel like this could be a great way to get some practice and make some cool new friends!
